    <link itemprop="mainEntityOfPage" href="liuxueyang.github.io/2012/11/07/uva-10790---How-Many-Points-of-Intersection?/">

    <span hidden itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
      <meta itemprop="name" content="liuxueyang">
